1
00:00:14,656 --> 00:00:18,240
♪Long and short,
sighs are whispers sharp as blades♪

2
00:00:18,976 --> 00:00:23,026
♪East and west, hustling and drifting
in the martial world♪

3
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:26,816
♪Destined or accidental,
no one falls for me♪

4
00:00:27,759 --> 00:00:31,232
♪Solitary is my middle name♪

5
00:00:32,064 --> 00:00:35,680
♪Spring after spring,
is the matchmaker dozing off♪

6
00:00:36,288 --> 00:00:39,872
♪You knock on the door of my heart,
a burst of blossoms amazing the dusk♪

7
00:00:40,576 --> 00:00:44,192
♪Touching or hurting,
we tacitly agree it's a kind of fortune♪

8
00:00:44,416 --> 00:00:48,867
♪The blue and the rosy
are heaven's match♪

9
00:00:49,504 --> 00:00:54,432
♪Falling into an embrace,
cherishing a moment of tenderness♪

10
00:00:54,624 --> 00:00:58,624
♪No need to mind at all
the blush on the cheeks♪

11
00:00:58,848 --> 00:01:02,944
♪Amid laughter and talk,
longing becomes words on the paper♪

12
00:01:03,488 --> 00:01:06,464
♪From now on, the delicate thoughts
speak no separation♪

13
00:01:06,464 --> 00:01:10,528
♪In the song that warms the world,
I only care for one person♪

14
00:01:10,528 --> 00:01:15,168
♪Before the autumn rain pours,
you hold the umbrella, and I wait♪

15
00:01:15,168 --> 00:01:19,264
♪Being deeply moved,
this life bears no regrets♪

16
00:01:19,264 --> 00:01:21,760
♪Flowers swaying,
we listen deep into the night♪

17
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:25,381
♪I wish the prime of youth favor you,
witnessed by the sun and moon♪

18
00:01:25,907 --> 00:01:31,497
=To Get Master=
(Based on The Fierce Princess by Jun Su)

19
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,992
=Episode 18=

20
00:01:41,660 --> 00:01:42,339
Han Yan,

21
00:01:42,660 --> 00:01:44,339
where are we going in such a hurry?

22
00:01:44,819 --> 00:01:45,819
To Riyue Palace.

23
00:01:46,140 --> 00:01:47,220
Riyue Palace?

24
00:01:47,580 --> 00:01:48,860
Gu Yuan won't go with us?

25
00:01:49,259 --> 00:01:50,940
The six major sects

26
00:01:51,059 --> 00:01:53,419
are gathering to fight
for the leader of martial world.

27
00:01:53,979 --> 00:01:55,100
My lord can't appear

28
00:01:55,220 --> 00:01:56,619
as Nan Chuimeng this time.

29
00:01:57,220 --> 00:02:00,059
A deadly battle is coming.

30
00:02:00,660 --> 00:02:03,140
So, he sent me to bring you back
to Riyue Palace.

31
00:02:03,539 --> 00:02:05,259
Once you're secure,

32
00:02:05,619 --> 00:02:07,539
he can focus on reclaiming
the Xiaoyao Technique.

33
00:02:08,740 --> 00:02:09,740
So, the villain

34
00:02:10,979 --> 00:02:13,100
will reclaim the Xiaoyao Technique

35
00:02:14,339 --> 00:02:15,339
as Gu Yuan?

36
00:02:16,540 --> 00:02:17,860
That's perfect.

37
00:02:18,820 --> 00:02:21,260
Hanging out with you guys,

38
00:02:21,499 --> 00:02:22,339
I've seen through

39
00:02:22,339 --> 00:02:23,619
those so-called righteous sects.

40
00:02:23,779 --> 00:02:25,619
They preach about honor and justice,

41
00:02:26,420 --> 00:02:28,300
but they're all full of hidden agendas.

42
00:02:34,659 --> 00:02:36,300
- Greetings, Leader.
- Greetings, Leader.

43
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:39,300
Please rise.

44
00:02:41,219 --> 00:02:42,219
Nan Wentian,

45
00:02:42,499 --> 00:02:44,059
why are you here?

46
00:02:46,099 --> 00:02:48,659
I came to congratulate
your enthronement.

47
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:51,540
If you don't want to see me,

48
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:52,980
I'll just go.

49
00:02:53,939 --> 00:02:55,059
Just stay.

50
00:02:55,899 --> 00:02:57,020
If you go,

51
00:02:57,659 --> 00:03:00,219
I'll suspect you of colluding
with the demon cult.

52
00:03:01,980 --> 00:03:03,379
How could that be possible?

53
00:03:05,779 --> 00:03:06,860
I wouldn't dare.

54
00:03:07,379 --> 00:03:10,140
Leader, you're a hero in the making.

55
00:03:10,260 --> 00:03:13,300
Your presence outshines even Mr. Wuya.

56
00:03:13,448 --> 00:03:15,099
You're truly your father's daughter.

57
00:03:24,499 --> 00:03:25,659
Master Nan

58
00:03:26,300 --> 00:03:28,420
is the paragon for us all.

59
00:03:28,740 --> 00:03:30,140
For the manual,

60
00:03:30,260 --> 00:03:32,260
you feigned paralysis
of both legs for years

61
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:35,260
and posed as the villain,
wreaking havoc everywhere.

62
00:03:35,460 --> 00:03:36,860
That level of dedication

63
00:03:37,860 --> 00:03:40,099
is truly admirable.

64
00:03:42,820 --> 00:03:43,820
Indeed.

65
00:03:44,659 --> 00:03:47,379
Leader, my painstaking efforts

66
00:03:47,580 --> 00:03:50,339
have now been fulfilled.

67
00:03:51,580 --> 00:03:54,339
You're old,
but not exactly thin-skinned.

68
00:03:55,059 --> 00:03:57,700
I've let you stay
in the Martial Alliance

69
00:03:57,820 --> 00:04:01,020
just because you've managed
Fengyu Valley for so long

70
00:04:01,420 --> 00:04:03,219
and contributed to the martial world.

71
00:04:03,899 --> 00:04:05,580
If you keep spouting nonsense,

72
00:04:05,779 --> 00:04:07,740
don't expect any mercy from me.

73
00:04:10,420 --> 00:04:11,860
He can really keep his composure.

74
00:04:16,619 --> 00:04:17,980
Leader, please don't be angry.

75
00:04:18,179 --> 00:04:19,179
I'm apologizing

76
00:04:19,580 --> 00:04:20,580
for him.

77
00:04:21,899 --> 00:04:22,899
The thing is,

78
00:04:23,460 --> 00:04:24,739
the villain Gu Yuan

79
00:04:25,180 --> 00:04:26,260
has already turned up.

80
00:04:26,820 --> 00:04:29,260
He's been hiding among us

81
00:04:29,779 --> 00:04:31,060
using the name Nan Chuimeng,

82
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:32,620
Master Nan's nephew.

83
00:04:33,020 --> 00:04:34,020
It's clear

84
00:04:34,180 --> 00:04:36,020
the demon cult
has been carefully planning

85
00:04:36,140 --> 00:04:38,979
to get the manual
and dominate the martial world.

86
00:04:41,380 --> 00:04:43,820
If we don't act fast, things could...

87
00:04:52,779 --> 00:04:54,539
So, please master the manual quickly

88
00:04:54,659 --> 00:04:55,940
and lead us to crush demon cult,

89
00:04:56,060 --> 00:04:57,620
to restore peace to the martial world!

90
00:04:58,739 --> 00:05:00,020
Of course!

91
00:05:00,419 --> 00:05:01,820
Rest easy.

92
00:05:02,580 --> 00:05:04,580
As long as I'm around,

93
00:05:06,020 --> 00:05:08,380
Gu Yuan won't get away.

94
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:12,099
- Great!
- Great!

95
00:05:12,940 --> 00:05:13,768
Good point!

96
00:05:13,768 --> 00:05:14,940
- Sounds good!
- You're right!

97
00:05:14,940 --> 00:05:15,940
You're right!

98
00:05:16,219 --> 00:05:17,899
- Great!
- Great!

99
00:05:18,020 --> 00:05:19,020
Great!

100
00:05:24,930 --> 00:05:29,480
(Guyue Inn)

101
00:05:36,380 --> 00:05:37,419
Hello, sirs...

102
00:05:38,539 --> 00:05:39,180
Gu Yuan!

103
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:40,460
Villain Gu Yuan!

104
00:05:58,580 --> 00:05:59,580
Serve the wine.

105
00:06:01,260 --> 00:06:02,260
Please come in.

106
00:06:07,452 --> 00:06:10,774
(Scent Travels Far)

107
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:46,219
We meet again.

108
00:06:54,380 --> 00:06:55,779
I am in a competition with someone.

109
00:06:56,219 --> 00:06:57,219
Do not disturb me.

110
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:05,979
Here comes another brat.

111
00:07:06,779 --> 00:07:07,779
Fisherman,

112
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:11,219
is this your backup?

113
00:07:15,219 --> 00:07:16,339
Fisherman,

114
00:07:16,779 --> 00:07:20,140
afraid of losing and call a lad?

115
00:07:29,500 --> 00:07:30,899
(The technique is all random,)

116
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:32,500
(but why is it so powerful?)

117
00:07:32,620 --> 00:07:34,219
You are pretty good.

118
00:07:43,659 --> 00:07:45,260
(Jingyun Manor?)

119
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:54,380
Senior,

120
00:07:54,460 --> 00:07:56,099
I apologize for my rudeness just now.

121
00:07:56,700 --> 00:07:58,419
May I ask your name?

122
00:07:58,539 --> 00:07:59,539
Phew, the cup's fine.

123
00:07:59,820 --> 00:08:01,140
My precious cup.

124
00:08:06,940 --> 00:08:08,380
You fisherman!

125
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:09,739
You cheated!

126
00:08:09,859 --> 00:08:12,380
I fell for this lad's trick!

127
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:13,500
I lost!

128
00:08:14,060 --> 00:08:15,380
We had a bet,

129
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:17,099
whoever stood up first loses,

130
00:08:17,219 --> 00:08:18,820
and I stood up! He didn't.

131
00:08:18,940 --> 00:08:20,140
So I lost!

132
00:08:20,979 --> 00:08:21,979
Alright.

133
00:08:25,299 --> 00:08:26,739
Take the book.

134
00:08:27,539 --> 00:08:28,219
Old fart,

135
00:08:28,339 --> 00:08:30,020
don't bother me again!

136
00:08:32,020 --> 00:08:33,020
Senior,

137
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:34,659
you're probably confused.

138
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:36,099
This seat was vacant just now.

139
00:08:45,580 --> 00:08:47,660
(He is a hidden master.)

140
00:08:49,979 --> 00:08:52,099
(What kind of book did he leave?)

141
00:08:58,492 --> 00:09:01,384
(Eternal Grace)

142
00:09:12,580 --> 00:09:15,820
Two families join,
a single bond of marriage.

143
00:09:16,180 --> 00:09:19,259
We become one in each other.

144
00:09:19,700 --> 00:09:23,780
Hearts intertwined.
Together for eternity.

145
00:09:26,339 --> 00:09:27,460
Bride,

146
00:09:27,780 --> 00:09:28,780
Li Song'er.

147
00:09:30,099 --> 00:09:31,219
Groom,

148
00:09:31,859 --> 00:09:33,180
Gu Yuan.

149
00:09:36,968 --> 00:09:38,139
(Marriage contract)

150
00:09:38,139 --> 00:09:40,700
This is truly our marriage contract.

151
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:44,099
Not Mengdie

152
00:09:44,940 --> 00:09:46,379
and Nan Chuimeng.

153
00:09:48,060 --> 00:09:49,499
It's Li Song'er

154
00:09:50,379 --> 00:09:51,859
and Gu Yuan!

155
00:10:12,700 --> 00:10:13,700
Li Song'er.

156
00:10:25,212 --> 00:10:27,144
(Integrity and Honor)

157
00:10:34,979 --> 00:10:35,979
Senior,

158
00:10:36,499 --> 00:10:38,099
you've been standing for an hour.

159
00:10:38,259 --> 00:10:40,940
Thinking too much is harmful.
Better to sit down.

160
00:10:42,859 --> 00:10:44,780
I've sat for decades.

161
00:10:45,180 --> 00:10:47,060
Standing up now is no big deal.

162
00:10:47,379 --> 00:10:48,700
Those wimps

163
00:10:48,979 --> 00:10:51,420
only dare to gossip behind my back.

164
00:10:51,940 --> 00:10:53,219
But in my face,

165
00:10:53,460 --> 00:10:54,460
who dares?

166
00:10:55,339 --> 00:10:56,420
Exactly!

167
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:59,499
Baili Xingchen
is also a good-for-nothing.

168
00:11:00,019 --> 00:11:01,379
Find someone to drive him out.

169
00:11:01,859 --> 00:11:03,259
I get mad just looking at him.

170
00:11:05,019 --> 00:11:07,739
Jingyun Manor
has the complete manual now.

171
00:11:08,259 --> 00:11:10,660
Our plans for decades are wasted.

172
00:11:13,180 --> 00:11:14,820
If we'd just made Chu Mengdie

173
00:11:14,940 --> 00:11:16,540
take the blame for killing Zhou Heng,

174
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:18,660
none of this would've happened!

175
00:11:21,099 --> 00:11:23,259
We need to think of a way now.

176
00:11:24,099 --> 00:11:25,099
Senior,

177
00:11:26,859 --> 00:11:28,580
I have something unclear.

178
00:11:29,979 --> 00:11:30,979
Why did you

179
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:35,180
arrange for Heng

180
00:11:38,019 --> 00:11:39,979
to marry into Fengyu Valley?

181
00:11:41,019 --> 00:11:42,019
That...

182
00:11:42,420 --> 00:11:44,060
That was because he was useful.

183
00:11:48,300 --> 00:11:50,420
Heng was loyal to Fengyu Valley.

184
00:11:51,139 --> 00:11:52,660
Even if he knew

185
00:11:53,619 --> 00:11:56,300
it was you, disguised as Gu Yuan,
stealing the manual,

186
00:11:57,700 --> 00:11:59,460
he'd keep quiet.

187
00:12:00,019 --> 00:12:01,580
Why did you have to go that far

188
00:12:02,420 --> 00:12:04,420
and kill him?

189
00:12:05,300 --> 00:12:06,300
How naive!

190
00:12:10,619 --> 00:12:13,540
A dead person
is far more useful than a living one.

191
00:12:14,060 --> 00:12:15,619
If I were as indecisive as you,

192
00:12:15,859 --> 00:12:17,339
would we be where we are today?

193
00:12:19,259 --> 00:12:21,219
Now that the valley's reputation
is at stake,

194
00:12:22,019 --> 00:12:23,339
we need to figure out a way

195
00:12:23,460 --> 00:12:25,739
to save the situation.
That's our main concern.

196
00:12:37,900 --> 00:12:38,900
Senior,

197
00:12:40,420 --> 00:12:41,619
should I have played...

198
00:12:42,099 --> 00:12:42,728
Was it

199
00:12:43,139 --> 00:12:44,219
black

200
00:12:44,820 --> 00:12:45,992
or white just now?

201
00:12:46,499 --> 00:12:47,619
Getting older

202
00:12:48,900 --> 00:12:50,780
really dulls the mind.

203
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:53,540
Sometimes I can't tell

204
00:12:54,900 --> 00:12:56,460
if white is better

205
00:12:57,499 --> 00:12:59,099
or black is better.

206
00:12:59,540 --> 00:13:00,660
Senior.

207
00:13:12,979 --> 00:13:13,979
My lord,

208
00:13:14,499 --> 00:13:16,540
you really give up
the Xiaoyao Technique?

209
00:13:21,700 --> 00:13:22,859
Sit down.

210
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:42,760
My lord,

211
00:13:43,259 --> 00:13:44,979
yesterday, you exposed

212
00:13:45,180 --> 00:13:46,900
Nan Wentian's hypocrisy publicly.

213
00:13:47,820 --> 00:13:49,139
But you shouldn't throw away

214
00:13:49,660 --> 00:13:51,339
the Xiaoyao Technique.

215
00:13:52,139 --> 00:13:54,540
You've been planning for ten years,
enduring so much pain,

216
00:13:54,728 --> 00:13:55,700
all to reclaim it

217
00:13:55,820 --> 00:13:56,859
one day.

218
00:13:57,540 --> 00:13:59,060
I just can't understand

219
00:13:59,859 --> 00:14:01,019
why you'd do this now.

220
00:14:01,499 --> 00:14:03,259
I think

221
00:14:03,820 --> 00:14:04,900
letting Nan Wentian live

222
00:14:05,300 --> 00:14:06,619
is the worst punishment for him.

223
00:14:07,300 --> 00:14:08,300
Back then,

224
00:14:08,540 --> 00:14:10,259
he stirred up the entire martial world,

225
00:14:10,580 --> 00:14:12,139
using those vicious methods

226
00:14:12,339 --> 00:14:13,580
to destroy Riyue Palace.

227
00:14:13,979 --> 00:14:15,019
Now

228
00:14:15,219 --> 00:14:17,420
he's ended up
being despised by everyone.

229
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:21,540
It's like what goes around,
comes around.

230
00:14:26,259 --> 00:14:27,780
Now that you've revealed your face

231
00:14:28,780 --> 00:14:30,820
and everyone knows who you are,

232
00:14:31,180 --> 00:14:32,180
I'm guessing

233
00:14:32,859 --> 00:14:34,180
you're in for a rough ride ahead.

234
00:14:35,739 --> 00:14:36,940
Back then, those people,

235
00:14:37,300 --> 00:14:38,619
to get the Xiaoyao Technique,

236
00:14:39,180 --> 00:14:41,580
lied that my parents
were using the manual

237
00:14:42,180 --> 00:14:43,859
to massacre the martial world.

238
00:14:44,780 --> 00:14:45,900
They framed Riyue Palace

239
00:14:46,859 --> 00:14:48,859
as the demon cult.

240
00:14:51,420 --> 00:14:52,780
After my parents were murdered,

241
00:14:54,180 --> 00:14:55,499
I went

242
00:14:56,300 --> 00:14:57,499
into hiding,

243
00:15:00,780 --> 00:15:02,139
living under this mask

244
00:15:03,019 --> 00:15:04,420
for more than 20 years.

245
00:15:07,900 --> 00:15:09,259
During these years,

246
00:15:10,780 --> 00:15:12,259
all I had was hate.

247
00:15:14,979 --> 00:15:16,580
All I wanted was to get the manual back

248
00:15:17,900 --> 00:15:19,420
and avenge my parents.

249
00:15:24,259 --> 00:15:25,619
Yesterday,

250
00:15:26,780 --> 00:15:28,700
seeing those so-called righteous sects

251
00:15:28,820 --> 00:15:29,900
and martial heroes

252
00:15:30,700 --> 00:15:32,060
acting like fools

253
00:15:32,499 --> 00:15:33,900
over the manual,

254
00:15:36,019 --> 00:15:37,859
I found it all so laughable.

255
00:15:39,859 --> 00:15:41,219
Suddenly, I realized

256
00:15:42,900 --> 00:15:44,219
that no matter what I did,

257
00:15:45,099 --> 00:15:46,540
I couldn't get back

258
00:15:47,339 --> 00:15:48,460
what I'd lost.

259
00:15:50,739 --> 00:15:52,219
And my obsessions

260
00:15:53,259 --> 00:15:54,460
were not crucial anymore.

261
00:15:56,780 --> 00:15:58,019
My towering anger

262
00:15:58,700 --> 00:16:00,060
all turned to falling flowers.

263
00:16:05,060 --> 00:16:06,619
After wearing this mask for so long,

264
00:16:07,660 --> 00:16:08,660
I'm just worn out.

265
00:16:27,580 --> 00:16:28,580
My lord!

266
00:16:28,859 --> 00:16:29,859
My lord!

267
00:16:48,420 --> 00:16:50,979
You silly oaf,
still playing with the lousy fork?

268
00:16:52,859 --> 00:16:55,180
Don't you think
you're still the Young Master

269
00:16:55,540 --> 00:16:57,820
of Fengyu Valley after losing
at the Houlang Conference?

270
00:16:58,580 --> 00:16:59,739
Jinx.

271
00:17:02,139 --> 00:17:03,460
Why do you

272
00:17:04,859 --> 00:17:05,900
mock me like this?

273
00:17:06,219 --> 00:17:07,219
Why?

274
00:17:07,700 --> 00:17:09,219
You're a complete waste.

275
00:17:10,019 --> 00:17:11,380
You had a clear path to the top.

276
00:17:11,620 --> 00:17:13,860
The leadership within reach,
and you just gave it away.

277
00:17:14,100 --> 00:17:15,299
What were you thinking?

278
00:17:16,779 --> 00:17:18,579
I can't fake it.

279
00:17:19,420 --> 00:17:21,019
What's the point

