Come on! So tiny!

566
00:33:17,180 --> 00:33:18,819
Every time I saw you before,

567
00:33:19,299 --> 00:33:22,100
you were always spirited and resolute,

568
00:33:23,140 --> 00:33:24,700
never letting anything get to you

569
00:33:25,100 --> 00:33:26,100
or touch your heart.

570
00:33:28,100 --> 00:33:29,100
Never thought

571
00:33:29,460 --> 00:33:30,460
I'd see you

572
00:33:31,420 --> 00:33:32,900
cry three times in just one day.

573
00:33:39,860 --> 00:33:41,140
I had given up hope

574
00:33:42,180 --> 00:33:44,180
of ever seeing Father again.

575
00:33:44,860 --> 00:33:45,979
Ten years ago,

576
00:33:46,499 --> 00:33:48,380
he left under the pretext of traveling.

577
00:33:49,539 --> 00:33:51,420
Initially, I got letters from him,

578
00:33:52,180 --> 00:33:54,779
but eventually, they just dried up.

579
00:33:56,660 --> 00:33:57,700
Over the years,

580
00:33:58,180 --> 00:33:59,180
I've sent disciples

581
00:33:59,299 --> 00:34:00,620
to search for him,

582
00:34:01,860 --> 00:34:03,299
but there was never any news.

583
00:34:05,340 --> 00:34:06,579
I thought...

584
00:34:07,940 --> 00:34:09,059
I've blamed him in the past.

585
00:34:10,499 --> 00:34:12,219
Why did he leave me behind?

586
00:34:13,019 --> 00:34:14,619
Why did he abandon the manor,

587
00:34:15,499 --> 00:34:17,059
making me shoulder the burden so early?

588
00:34:19,099 --> 00:34:20,099
I've resented him

589
00:34:20,780 --> 00:34:21,780
and hated him.

590
00:34:22,940 --> 00:34:24,059
But even so,

591
00:34:25,300 --> 00:34:26,900
if he doesn't recognize me now,

592
00:34:29,099 --> 00:34:30,220
as his child,

593
00:34:30,740 --> 00:34:32,179
I should also ensure his safety.

594
00:34:39,099 --> 00:34:40,780
As the leader of martial world,

595
00:34:41,340 --> 00:34:42,619
I truly see.

596
00:34:43,380 --> 00:34:45,659
In the Jianghu,
we are but leaves in the wind,

597
00:34:46,139 --> 00:34:47,579
carried where we can't choose.

598
00:34:48,979 --> 00:34:50,499
You mean

599
00:34:51,059 --> 00:34:52,460
wiping out Riyue Palace?

600
00:34:52,979 --> 00:34:55,019
It's just the beginning.

601
00:34:56,179 --> 00:34:57,260
In the years ahead,

602
00:34:57,780 --> 00:35:00,220
who knows how many more things
I'll be forced to do?

603
00:35:02,300 --> 00:35:03,780
I'm afraid

604
00:35:04,380 --> 00:35:06,460
I won't be able
to judge right from wrong.

605
00:35:09,740 --> 00:35:10,900
Don't be troubled.

606
00:35:11,539 --> 00:35:13,139
I trust you.

607
00:35:13,420 --> 00:35:15,099
You won't let any villain
escape justice,

608
00:35:15,539 --> 00:35:16,659
and you won't harm

609
00:35:16,979 --> 00:35:18,420
any innocent.

610
00:35:22,460 --> 00:35:24,979
Instead of worrying,

611
00:35:25,499 --> 00:35:27,539
just work on your skills.

612
00:35:28,940 --> 00:35:31,780
In the Jianghu, only the strong

613
00:35:32,860 --> 00:35:34,860
can truly judge right from wrong.

614
00:35:36,220 --> 00:35:37,220
Father,

615
00:35:38,579 --> 00:35:40,139
have you remembered everything?

616
00:35:45,260 --> 00:35:46,260
This is fun!

617
00:35:46,460 --> 00:35:48,139
T-This is so fun!

618
00:35:48,579 --> 00:35:50,220
So amazing!

619
00:35:55,179 --> 00:35:55,780
Come on!

620
00:35:55,780 --> 00:35:57,380
I can't leave him

621
00:35:59,139 --> 00:36:01,340
like this, no matter what.

622
00:36:04,260 --> 00:36:05,260
Baili,

623
00:36:05,659 --> 00:36:06,499
can you...?

624
00:36:06,619 --> 00:36:07,619
Don't worry.

625
00:36:08,059 --> 00:36:08,840
I was planning

626
00:36:09,099 --> 00:36:10,900
to stick around for a while.

627
00:36:11,499 --> 00:36:12,699
I'll look after them.

628
00:36:14,900 --> 00:36:16,300
When my matter is settled,

629
00:36:17,099 --> 00:36:18,579
I'll return to you.

630
00:36:44,059 --> 00:36:45,059
Song'er,

631
00:36:45,380 --> 00:36:46,380
Master's in the pavilion.

632
00:36:46,579 --> 00:36:47,900
It's something important.

633
00:36:48,380 --> 00:36:49,380
I'll handle the medicine.

634
00:36:50,380 --> 00:36:51,380
In an hour,

635
00:36:51,460 --> 00:36:52,460
add some water.

636
00:36:54,019 --> 00:36:55,019
Cold water.

637
00:36:55,139 --> 00:36:56,139
I'll go.

638
00:37:07,820 --> 00:37:08,820
Gu Yuan,

639
00:37:09,019 --> 00:37:10,900
I know you can't wait to see me,

640
00:37:11,659 --> 00:37:13,380
but you need to get better first.

641
00:37:17,860 --> 00:37:18,860
It's so cold outside.

642
00:37:19,059 --> 00:37:20,059
What if you catch a cold

643
00:37:20,220 --> 00:37:21,499
and be even sicker?

644
00:37:25,099 --> 00:37:26,099
Song'er,

645
00:37:28,220 --> 00:37:30,380
it's time to leave.

646
00:37:31,460 --> 00:37:32,659
Leave?

647
00:37:47,049 --> 00:37:49,281
♪Wherever the wind blows♪

648
00:37:49,681 --> 00:37:53,481
♪I share day and night with you♪

649
00:37:53,881 --> 00:37:56,001
♪No matter what lies ahead♪

650
00:37:56,441 --> 00:37:59,761
♪Be it clashing blades
or the mundane world♪

651
00:38:00,521 --> 00:38:02,681
♪The wind blows away the fog♪

652
00:38:03,041 --> 00:38:06,921
♪In a glance, I look into your eyes♪

653
00:38:07,281 --> 00:38:13,281
♪Not regretting
my solitariness in this life♪

654
00:38:13,921 --> 00:38:16,761
♪Never looking back
to find the way home♪

655
00:38:17,121 --> 00:38:20,121
♪Why be confused about where to go♪

656
00:38:20,521 --> 00:38:26,161
♪A thousand threads of love
prevent me from stepping back♪

657
00:38:27,241 --> 00:38:30,161
♪As winter passes,
frost flowers penetrate the bone♪

658
00:38:30,521 --> 00:38:33,481
♪With spring's arrival,
longing colors the morning dew♪

659
00:38:33,841 --> 00:38:39,601
♪Fortunate to express
infinite affection to someone♪

660
00:38:40,481 --> 00:38:43,561
♪Better to draw a sword and dance
and write a book for you♪

661
00:38:43,921 --> 00:38:46,521
♪We can run towards the future♪

662
00:38:47,121 --> 00:38:50,241
♪Better not to speak of despair
but compose for love instead♪

663
00:38:50,665 --> 00:38:53,561
♪Do not fail the past♪

664
00:38:53,961 --> 00:38:56,801
♪Better to be as initial as time fleets♪

665
00:38:57,121 --> 00:39:00,041
♪Everything turns to dust♪

666
00:39:00,401 --> 00:39:06,569
♪In this life's ups and downs,
you are the home♪

667
00:39:07,145 --> 00:39:13,041
♪In this life's ups and downs,
you are the home♪
